headline: UBS Increases Fair Isaac (FICO) PT to $1,590 After Strong Q3 Performance From Scores Segment Growth
summary: Fair Isaac Corporation (NYSE:FICO) is one of the stocks to invest in before they split next. On September 8, UBS raised the firm’s price target on FICO to $1,590 from $1,540, while keeping a Neutral rating on the shares.
